{
 "name": "RPlog_Nexu_Hunting_-_Part_1",
 "title": "Nexu Hunting (Part 1)",
 "summary": "In the early morning aboard OS Paladin, Marines and pilots are assembled for a dangerous hunt: the deadly Nexu that escaped from a cargo container are now loose and breeding in the station's maintenance tunnels. Lt. Commander Maggrath and the Bith technician Ohao brief the team, including the limping Lieutenant Vengan, Sergeant Tal'sin Secura, Staff Sergeant Mason, and the nervous young pilot Raxis, arming them with shotguns and stun-set blasters. Tal'sin leads the hunting party, designated Bandit Bravo, into the tunnels while Vengan coordinates from a command station. Deep in the station's bowels, a great gray Nexu and its mate guard their newborn cubs, sensing the approaching threat.",
